These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, fisherman, manager, designer
1. the designer is on the left or right of the scientist##3
2. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
3. the fisherman is not to the left of the manager##8
4. the fisherman is on the left of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Job   | manager | fisherman | designer | scientist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, juice
1. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | sprite | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, spinach, kiwi, garlic
1. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5
2. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
3. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | cucumber | garlic | spinach | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, cooking, collecting, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | cooking | singing | collecting | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, golf, basketball, sailing
