2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
3. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |       3       |    4     |
| Sport   | golf | basketball | sailing | cricket |

