2. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating kale is not to the left of the person eating pomegranate##8
4. the person eating kale is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |     3     |   4   |
| Food   | potato | pomegranate | kale | artichoke |

